hopobject.body: There's a three month trial period is over the counter nexium the same strength as prescription nexium Some big users of foreign work visas will not be subject to the new restrictions. Companies such as Microsoft, which finds most of its foreign engineers on American college campuses, will not have to register its recruiters with the government. The restrictions will mostly target international outsourcing firms, such as Infosys and Wipro, that secure the visas and provide their workers to U.S. companies.
